version_description:
[Fixed] 
– Players’ status wasn’t displayed correctly in history of matches;
– Game files downloading issues;
– Problems with equipment display in a spectator mode; 
– Sometimes hands or weapons weren’t displayed correctly in a spectator mode;
– Some other details making the game more comfortable to play. 

[Changes]
– Clan leader can’t leave a clan now until there are other players in it;
– New Year 2021 collection filter is added.

