• Added a new value to the target framerate settings: 90 fps;
• Added the ability to adjust the voice chat volume;
• Changed the interface for selecting a weapon in Assault and Escalation modes;
• Upped the XP gain for winning in Assault mode;
• Fixed multiple bugs;
• Improved general game optimization.
• Fixed voice chat issues on Apple devices;
• Discontinued support for iPhone 5 and iPhone 5c;

